---
title: Black Bean Croquette Tapas Plates with Paprika Potatoes and Red Pepper Mayo
description: Tonight, take a trip to Spain with this tapas-inspired plate. There's no need to get on a plane when you can have crispy bean croquettes, patatas bravas-style paprika-dusted potatoes and a roasted red pepper salad, all in the comfort of your own home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/black-bean-croquette-tapas-plates-ac40e63e.jpg
